<h2>Shape Generator</h2>
<p>Please enter what shape you would to generate.</p>
<p>Here are some examples:</p>
<ul>
  <li><i>Draw a circle with a radius of 100</i></li>
  <li><i>Draw a square with a side length of 200</i></li>
  <li><i>Draw a rectangle with a width of 250 and a height of 400</i></li>
  <li><i>Draw an octagon witha side length of 200</i></li>
  <li><i>Draw an isosceles triangle with a height of 200 and width of 100</i></li>
</ul>
